*Osiguranja* su potrebna da bi se postigla sigurnost. (Insurance is needed to achieve security.)

Svi smo se *osigurali* od mogućih rizika. (We all insured ourselves from potential risks.)

Tržište *osiguranja* je postalo veoma konkurentno. (The insurance market has become very competitive.)

Naša kompanija je lider u oblasti *osiguranja*. (Our company is a leader in the field of insurance.)

*Osiguravamo* se od neželjenih posledica. (We are insuring ourselves from undesired consequences.)